<template>
    <v-container
    class="fill-height"
    fluid
    >
        <v-row
        align="center"
        justify="center"
        >
            <v-col
                cols="12"
                sm="8"
                lg="4"
                xl="4"
                md="6"
            >
                <v-card class="elevation-12">
                <v-toolbar
                    color="primary"
                    dark
                    flat
                >
                    <v-toolbar-title>Вход</v-toolbar-title>
                </v-toolbar>
                <v-card-text>
                    <v-alert
                    dense
                    border="left"
                    type="warning"
                    >
                        Error
                    </v-alert>
                    <v-form @submit.prevent="onSubmit">
                    <v-text-field
                        label="E-mail"
                        name="email"
                        prepend-icon="mdi-account"
                        type="email"
                        required
                    ></v-text-field>

                    <v-text-field
                        id="password"
                        label="Пароль"
                        name="password"
                        prepend-icon="mdi-lock"
                        type="password"
                        required
                    ></v-text-field>
                    <v-card-actions>
                        <router-link to="/signup" class="text--primary">Зарегистрироваться</router-link>
                        <v-spacer></v-spacer>
                        <v-btn color="primary" type="submit">Войти</v-btn>
                    </v-card-actions>
                    </v-form>
                </v-card-text>
                </v-card>
            </v-col>
        </v-row>
    </v-container>
</template>

<script>
export default {
    name: 'Login',
    methods: {
        onSubmit(){
            this.$router.push('/')
        }
    }
}
</script>
